preference.name: TC_LAST_USED_PATTERNS
preference.preference_description: Stores the last selected naming pattern for a given business object property. The values will be set when Naming Rules are used for different operations. This preference is not meant to be modified manually. Valid Values: Accepts one or more strings as values, each string must be a valid naming pattern.
